<i>adverb</i>: 하염없이 [하여멉씨], 종알종알 [종알종알], 끊임없이 [끄니멉씨] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>하염없이 [하여멉씨]</dt><br>
<dd>1. absent-mindedly; blankly; vacantly</dd><br>
<dd>걱정에 싸여 아무 생각이 없이 멍하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Absent-mindedly without any thoughts, being worried about something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. endlessly; incessantly</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 행동이나 감정 등이 그치지 않고 계속되는 상태로.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which a certain act or emotion continues without stopping.</dd><br>
<dt>종알종알 [종알종알]</dt><br>
<dd>incessantly</dd><br>
<dd>주로 여자나 아이들이 남이 알아듣지 못할 정도의 작은 목소리로 혼잣말을 자꾸 하는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>Generally, in such a manner that a woman or child keeps talking to himself/herself in so small a voice that others cannot hear.</dd><br>
<dt>끊임없이 [끄니멉씨]</dt><br>
<dd>incessantly; unceasingly; ceaselessly</dd><br>
<dd>계속하거나 이어져 있던 것이 끊이지 아니하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that something that has been continued or connected is not interrupted.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>